OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,FHollywood star Alan Cumming has
OL,8,Fsubmitted a costume he wore while
OL,9,Fhosting the US version of The Traitors
OL,10,Fto the V&A Dundee as it launches a
OL,11,Fcall for people to lend treasured
OL,12,Fobjects to go on show.
OL,14,FThe museum is inviting people to help
OL,15,Ftell the story of Scottish design by
OL,16,Fsubmitting items for display from 2028
OL,17,Fin the museum's reimagined Scottish
OL,18,FDesign Galleries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
