PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,FCumming has submitted the first
OL,8,Fobject, a costume from The Traitors
OL,9,FUS, along with one worn by his dog
OL,10,FLala.
OL,12,FThe outfit, from season four of the
OL,13,Fshow, was created by Scottish designer
OL,14,FSiobhan Mackenzie in collaboration
OL,15,Fwith costume designer Sam Spector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,FIt features a tartan chest plate with
OL,8,Fa crystal sgian dubh knife impaling
OL,9,Fthe heart area, which is surrounded by
OL,10,Fa red crystal "wound", a matching
OL,11,Ftartan kilt and a sweeping metallic
OL,12,Fred silk chiffon plaid.
OL,14,FCumming, also known for roles
OL,15,Fincluding Nightcrawler in the Avengers
OL,16,Ffilm series, said: "I love this
OL,17,FSiobhan Mackenzie look so much because
OL,18,Fit's got all these things I love about
OL,19,FScotland in it: tradition, daring,
OL,20,Fromanticism, camp and theatricality
OL,21,Fall rolled into one.
OL,26,@rD@OOUrD@UO]xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,F"V&A Dundee, to me, stands for
OL,8,FScottish excellence in design and the
OL,9,Farts. I think what we're really good
OL,10,Fat in Scotland is staying in touch
OL,11,Fwith our tradition but also looking to
OL,12,Fthe future and being progressive in
OL,13,Fterms of what we see as our
OL,14,FScottishness in the now.
OL,16,F"It's lovely to be part of a
OL,17,Fcelebration of Scottish excellence and
OL,18,Falso, of course, my dog Lala's outfit
OL,19,Fbeing in the galleries too is just the
OL,20,Ficing on the cake.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,F"So everybody, what would you like to
OL,8,Fsee at V&A Dundee? What Scottish
OL,9,Fdesign object would you like to see
OL,10,Fdisplayed there and why?
OL,12,F"We really, really want to hear from
OL,13,Fyou ` it's your museum, after all `
OL,14,Fand what you'd like to see represented
OL,15,Ffrom the world of Scottish design."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,FThe museum is urging people to submit
OL,8,Fitems that make them think of Scotland
OL,9,Fand what it means to be Scottish,
OL,10,Fwhich could be anything from pieces of
OL,11,Fclothing to personal souvenirs and
OL,12,Ffamily keepsakes.
OL,14,FIt said no object or story is too
OL,15,Fsmall or too big to be submitted on
OL,16,Floan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,FLeonie Bell, director of V&A Dundee,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We want to hear from you. V&A
OL,9,FDundee is Scotland's design museum and
OL,10,Fwe want to share many different
OL,11,Fstories of Scotland that are told
OL,12,Fthrough the objects we hold dear.
OL,14,F"From the most cherished keepsakes to
OL,15,Fthe fashion of your rebellious youth,
OL,16,Fwe want to represent what Scotland
OL,17,Fmeans to you through the objects that
OL,18,Fyou have collected through your lives.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,F"How does the object make you feel?
OL,8,FWhat memories does it bring back, or
OL,9,Fwhat wishes does it hold for the
OL,10,Ffuture? Does the item reflect your
OL,11,Fpersonal or a collective identity?
OL,13,F"We want to open up the range of
OL,14,Fdesign on display so that all our
OL,15,Fvisitors can enjoy a wider, more
OL,16,Finspiring look into the many different
OL,17,Fcommunities and people that make
OL,18,FScotland so diverse, vibrant and
OL,19,Fcreative."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1783639110
OL,3,CAlan Cumming submits Traitors US
OL,4,Coutfit to V&A Dundee's Scottish design
OL,5,Cdisplay
OL,7,FThe objects chosen to go on display
OL,8,Fwhen the redesigned galleries open in
OL,9,F2028 will be co-curated by V&A Dundee
OL,10,Fand a community panel.
OL,12,FSubmissions of personal objects to be
OL,13,Fincluded can be made by email to
OL,14,Fmyobject@vandadundee.org until August
OL,15,F31.
OL,17,FThe redesign is supported by #2.6
OL,18,Fmillion of UK Government funding and
OL,19,Fadditional private fundraising.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
